ЁЯУЭ Summary (English)

There are N friends.

1 subscription can be shared by 6 people.

Cost of 1 subscription = X rupees.

We need to find minimum total cost so that all N friends get Chef-TV.

ЁЯСЙ Formula:

Subscriptions needed = ceil(N / 6) = (N + 5) / 6 (using integer math).

Total cost = Subscriptions ├Ч X.

